'''天主教和平港教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Portus Pacis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Port-de-Paix}}）是[[海地|海地]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教海地角總教區|海地角總教區]]。

教區於1861年10月3日成立，2004年時有330,000名教友，佔轄區總人口60.0%。教區下轄十七個堂區，有卅五名司鐸。

現任教區主教為{{link-de|嘉祿·伯多祿·巴爾泰呂|Charles Peters Barthélus}}<ref name="Vatican20200414">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 14.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/14/200414a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416063725/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/14/200414a.html |archivedate=2020-04-16 |language=en |date=2020-04-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-fr|方濟各·科利蒙|François Colimon}}和{{link-en|伯多祿-安多尼·波洛|Pierre-Antoine Paulo}}<ref name="Vatican20200414" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 01.03.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/03/01/0146/00329.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416080445/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/03/01/0146/00329.html |archivedate=2020-04-16 |language=it |date=2008-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

